Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Instate, International, Outstate

    public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    The student class stores the first name, last name, and credit of a student. It also implements a compareTo methods, toString method, and an abstract tuitionDue method, that is to be implemented in a child class.
    Author:
    Brandon Trastoy, Kyle VanWageninge
